import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score

# Membaca hasil prediksi untuk setiap model
models = ["RN5O", "ViT-B/16", "ViT-L/14", "ViT-B32"]
model_paths = [
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model RN5O.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTB16.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTL14.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTB32.csv"
]

# Fungsi untuk membersihkan dan menormalkan prediksi
def clean_predicted_time(predicted_time):
    return predicted_time.rstrip('.')  # Menghapus titik di akhir kata jika ada

def normalize_predicted_place(predicted_place):
    place_mapping = {
        "the field": "in the field",
        "the hill": "on the hill",
        "the forrest": "in the forrest" 
    }
    return place_mapping.get(predicted_place, predicted_place)  # Default ke prediksi asli jika tidak ada di mapping

# Membaca file Excel untuk ground truth
ground_truth_excel_path = r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\dataset_class_clip.xlsx"
ground_truth_df = pd.read_excel(ground_truth_excel_path)

# Memastikan kolom-kolom ground truth ada dalam file Excel
ground_truth_dict = dict(zip(ground_truth_df["Image"], ground_truth_df[["Animal", "Behavior", "Place", "Time"]].values))

# List untuk menyimpan hasil akurasi per model
accuracy_results = []

# Membaca dan menganalisis setiap model
for model_path in model_paths:
    model_df = pd.read_csv(model_path)
    
    # Menormalkan prediksi Place dan Time
    model_df["Predicted Place"] = model_df["Predicted Place"].apply(normalize_predicted_place)
    model_df["Predicted Time"] = model_df["Predicted Time"].apply(clean_predicted_time)
    
    # Menyiapkan label ground truth untuk perbandingan
    true_labels_animal = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][0] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    true_labels_behavior = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][1] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    true_labels_place = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][2] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    true_labels_time = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][3] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    
    # Prediksi per kategori
    predicted_labels_animal = model_df["Predicted Animal"]
    predicted_labels_behavior = model_df["Predicted Behavior"]
    predicted_labels_place = model_df["Predicted Place"]
    predicted_labels_time = model_df["Predicted Time"]
    
    # Menghitung akurasi per kategori untuk model ini
    accuracy_animal = accuracy_score(true_labels_animal, predicted_labels_animal)
    accuracy_behavior = accuracy_score(true_labels_behavior, predicted_labels_behavior)
    accuracy_place = accuracy_score(true_labels_place, predicted_labels_place)
    accuracy_time = accuracy_score(true_labels_time, predicted_labels_time)
    
    # Menyimpan hasil akurasi untuk model ini
    accuracy_results.append([accuracy_animal, accuracy_behavior, accuracy_place, accuracy_time])

# Mengonversi hasil akurasi ke dalam DataFrame untuk kemudahan analisis
accuracy_df = pd.DataFrame(accuracy_results, columns=["Animal", "Behavior", "Place", "Time"], index=models)

# Menampilkan DataFrame akurasi per model
print("Accuracy Comparison Table:")
print(accuracy_df)

# Plot heatmap perbandingan akurasi antar model
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 7))
sns.heatmap(accuracy_df, annot=True, cmap="Blues", fmt=".2f", cbar_kws={'label': 'Accuracy'}, linewidths=0.5)
plt.title("Accuracy Comparison Heatmap")
plt.ylabel("Model")
plt.xlabel("Category")
plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score

# Membaca hasil prediksi untuk setiap model
models = ["RN5O", "ViT-B/16", "ViT-L/14", "ViT-B32"]
model_paths = [
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model RN5O.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTB16.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTL14.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTB32.csv"
]

# Fungsi untuk membersihkan dan menormalkan prediksi
def clean_predicted_time(predicted_time):
    return predicted_time.rstrip('.')  # Menghapus titik di akhir kata jika ada

def normalize_predicted_place(predicted_place):
    place_mapping = {
        "the field": "in the field",
        "the hill": "on the hill",
        "the forrest": "in the forrest" 
    }
    return place_mapping.get(predicted_place, predicted_place)  # Default ke prediksi asli jika tidak ada di mapping

# Membaca file Excel untuk ground truth
ground_truth_excel_path = r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\dataset_class_clip.xlsx"
ground_truth_df = pd.read_excel(ground_truth_excel_path)

# Memastikan kolom-kolom ground truth ada dalam file Excel
ground_truth_dict = dict(zip(ground_truth_df["Image"], ground_truth_df[["Animal", "Behavior", "Place", "Time"]].values))

# Daftar kategori yang akan dianalisis
animals = ["cow", "goat", "sheep"]
behaviors = ["eating", "moving", "resting"]
places = ["in the field", "on the hill", "in the forrest"]
times = ["day", "night"]

# Daftar kategori yang akan digunakan untuk perhitungan akurasi spesifik
categories = animals + behaviors + places + times

# List untuk menyimpan hasil akurasi per model
accuracy_results = []

# Membaca dan menganalisis setiap model
for model_path in model_paths:
    model_df = pd.read_csv(model_path)
    
    # Menormalkan prediksi Place dan Time
    model_df["Predicted Place"] = model_df["Predicted Place"].apply(normalize_predicted_place)
    model_df["Predicted Time"] = model_df["Predicted Time"].apply(clean_predicted_time)
    
    # Menyiapkan label ground truth untuk perbandingan
    true_labels_animal = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][0] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    true_labels_behavior = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][1] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    true_labels_place = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][2] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    true_labels_time = [ground_truth_dict[image_name][3] for image_name in model_df["Image"]]
    
    # Prediksi per kategori
    predicted_labels_animal = model_df["Predicted Animal"]
    predicted_labels_behavior = model_df["Predicted Behavior"]
    predicted_labels_place = model_df["Predicted Place"]
    predicted_labels_time = model_df["Predicted Time"]
    
    # Menyimpan akurasi untuk setiap kategori
    accuracy_per_category = {}
    
    # Akurasi untuk kategori Animal (cow, sheep, goat)
    for animal in animals:
        true_animal = [1 if x == animal else 0 for x in true_labels_animal]
        predicted_animal = [1 if x == animal else 0 for x in predicted_labels_animal]
        accuracy_per_category[f"Animal_{animal}"] = accuracy_score(true_animal, predicted_animal)
    
    # Akurasi untuk kategori Behavior (moving, eating, resting)
    for behavior in behaviors:
        true_behavior = [1 if x == behavior else 0 for x in true_labels_behavior]
        predicted_behavior = [1 if x == behavior else 0 for x in predicted_labels_behavior]
        accuracy_per_category[f"Behavior_{behavior}"] = accuracy_score(true_behavior, predicted_behavior)
    
    # Akurasi untuk kategori Place (in the field, on the hill, in the forrest)
    for place in places:
        true_place = [1 if x == place else 0 for x in true_labels_place]
        predicted_place = [1 if x == place else 0 for x in predicted_labels_place]
        accuracy_per_category[f"Place_{place}"] = accuracy_score(true_place, predicted_place)
    
    # Akurasi untuk kategori Time (day, night)
    for time in times:
        true_time = [1 if x == time else 0 for x in true_labels_time]
        predicted_time = [1 if x == time else 0 for x in predicted_labels_time]
        accuracy_per_category[f"Time_{time}"] = accuracy_score(true_time, predicted_time)
    
    # Menyimpan hasil akurasi untuk model ini
    accuracy_results.append(accuracy_per_category)

# Mengonversi hasil akurasi ke dalam DataFrame untuk kemudahan analisis
accuracy_df = pd.DataFrame(accuracy_results, index=models)

# Menampilkan DataFrame akurasi per model dan kategori
print("Accuracy Comparison Table:")
print(accuracy_df)

# Plot heatmap perbandingan akurasi antar model
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
sns.heatmap(accuracy_df, annot=True, cmap="Blues", fmt=".2f", cbar_kws={'label': 'Accuracy'}, linewidths=0.5)
plt.title("Accuracy Comparison Heatmap per Category")
plt.ylabel("Model")
plt.xlabel("Category")
plt.xticks(rotation=90)  # Rotate category labels for better readability
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

# Daftar model dan path file CSV
models = ["RN5O", "ViT-B/16", "ViT-L/14", "ViT-B32"]
model_paths = [
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model RN5O.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTB16.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTL14.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\Model ViTB32.csv"
]

# Membaca dan mengolah distribusi teks prediksi untuk setiap model
distribution_results = {}

for model_name, model_path in zip(models, model_paths):
    # Membaca file CSV model
    model_df = pd.read_csv(model_path)
    
    # Menghitung frekuensi kemunculan setiap 'Prediction Sentence'
    sentence_counts = model_df['Prediction Sentence'].value_counts()
    
    # Menyimpan hasil distribusi teks per model
    distribution_results[model_name] = sentence_counts

    # Menampilkan 5 prediksi paling sering untuk model ini
    print(f"\nDistribusi Teks Prediksi untuk Model {model_name}:")
    print(sentence_counts.head(10))

# Membuat subplot grid untuk visualisasi
fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(16, 12))
axes = axes.flatten()

for i, model_name in enumerate(models):
    model_data = distribution_results[model_name].head(10)  # Ambil 10 prediksi terbanyak
    sns.barplot(
        x=model_data.values,
        y=model_data.index,
        ax=axes[i],
        palette="viridis"
    )
    axes[i].set_title(f"Top 10 Prediksi untuk Model {model_name}")
    axes[i].set_xlabel("Frequency")
    axes[i].set_ylabel("Prediction Sentence")

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

# Daftar path file CSV
model_paths = [
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\confidence_values_ViTL14.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\confidence_values_Vitb32.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\confidence_values_RN50.csv",
    r"C:\Users\USER\Documents\Semester 7\DL\Tubes\Data Tubes DL\Dataset\confidence_values_vitb16.csv"
]

# Nama model yang sesuai dengan path
model_names = ["ViTL14", "Vitb32", "RN50", "Vitb16"]

# Fungsi untuk memproses dan mengekstrak nilai confidence
def process_confidence_values(df):
    # Mengonversi nilai dalam format string array menjadi nilai numerik
    for col in ["Confidence Animal", "Confidence Behavior", "Confidence Place", "Confidence Time"]:
        df[col] = df[col].apply(lambda x: np.array(eval(x)))  # Mengambil array numpy
    return df

# Membaca dan memproses setiap model
confidence_data = {}
for model_path, model_name in zip(model_paths, model_names):
    # Membaca CSV
    df = pd.read_csv(model_path)
    # Proses nilai confidence untuk setiap model
    processed_df = process_confidence_values(df)
    
    # Simpan nilai confidence per kategori per gambar
    confidence_data[model_name] = {
        "Animal": processed_df["Confidence Animal"].explode(),
        "Behavior": processed_df["Confidence Behavior"].explode(),
        "Place": processed_df["Confidence Place"].explode(),
        "Time": processed_df["Confidence Time"].explode()
    }

# Visualisasi distribusi menggunakan histogram
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 10))

# Membuat subplot untuk setiap kategori
categories = ["Animal", "Behavior", "Place", "Time"]
for i, category in enumerate(categories, 1):
    plt.subplot(2, 2, i)
    
    # Plot histogram untuk setiap model pada kategori tersebut
    for model_name in model_names:
        sns.histplot(confidence_data[model_name][category], kde=True, label=model_name, bins=10)
    
    # Menambahkan judul dan label
    plt.title(f'Distribution of Confidence for {category}')
    plt.xlabel('Confidence Value')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend()

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
